{"id":"f35e03c7-41b8-4bbc-b2e6-d22a5c127f65","name":"Kagetsu","description":"<p>Ivy's retainer and an affable soldier from the royal castle of Elusia. He enjoys sparring and dining on the cuisine of Pale Sands. Appears in Fire Emblem Engage.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wh7lv1E-Z5dhLuUF99P5B.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 500px; height: auto\" class=\"\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kagetsu is a royal knight of Elusia. An amiable Hero with a distinctive style of speech, he’s also a first-class swordmaster!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1LlGeFkn9piiwcx8VCTgh.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 500px; height: auto\" class=\"\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kagetsu was born in the secluded Pale Sands of northeastern Solm. Apparently, he left home hoping to learn about the outside world.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/zxv3EoJFiuVkBCnde6_8Q.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 500px; height: auto\" class=\"\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">His travels took him to Elusia Castle, where he challenged the royal knights in pursuit of a worthy opponent! Having made an impression, he was then made a retainer to Ivy, the crown princess.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Rayr10_jn417Kw6azjb_V.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 500px; height: auto\" class=\"\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Well, Kagetsu, if you’re looking for strong warriors, look no further than the Order of Heroes! Ah, I can hear him cheerfully throwing down the gauntlet already!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/rhp8CMUn0fJuugMEYoZkG.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 500px; height: auto\" class=\"\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Full Art By: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://feheroes.fandom.com/wiki/PenekoR\" target=\"_blank\">PenekoR (п猫R)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7iX__xoK4pJyGSSSvTX25.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 500px; height: auto\" class=\"\"></span></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"ffw6jB4TFMrrSIe1pTxtu.webp","creator":"Denki_The_Thunder_King27","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":14,"messages":1010,"created_at":"2026-04-01T17:56:22.979305+00:00"}